mg src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9feff1ff461009c21104d420280d5eee69260d8","tid":2137670,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:43:17.000Z","msg":"用人民幣買石油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2be2e278ebe0ce62b41e6299fc52b36b12ab7f","tid":2137670,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:47:48.000Z","msg":"支那要再買多啲大豆，買哂美帝既野<br />\n咁咪贏囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d31ded9b56be63d7fb094d127bcabd2227d12d9","tid":2137670,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"你叫強國收返自已D廢紙想佢死咩,其心可誅"},{"pid":"60459c39016e194c26d0aa03bdc77e162e047915","tid":2137670,"uid":258106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89066ea18ea4445803ba83bbcdc69593c7aebcce","tid":2137670,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"買聖誕卡用人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:50:23.000Z","msg":"屍永青聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【奶共左報】彭博（Bloomberg）出左news 話中共幫香港起臨時醫院<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2137847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2137847</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cad768d1e78935f8cab82e364bf3ef342453a8f9","tid":2137670,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"貪官話 你肯我唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src